<subSubSection id="79C665300B7B7B1CFF724DBD3021BA19" pageId="16" pageNumber="17" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="316336BB0B7B7B1CFF724DBD3021BA19" blockId="16.[151,1437,151,1844]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">
<emphasis id="03A8EAA90B7B7B1CFF724DBD352EBA25" bold="true" box="[197,313,1783,1807]" pageId="16" pageNumber="17">Remarks.</emphasis>
The number of marginal spines on the signum has not been quantified exactly, because we have only one female specimen of the species. This number is likely to vary intraspecifically.
